<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Welcome to Qurieus</title>
  <style>
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      max-width: 600px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      padding: 20px;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 30px;
    }
    .content {
      background-color: #f9f9f9;
      padding: 20px;
      border-radius: 5px;
    }
    .details {
      margin: 20px 0;
    }
    .details ul {
      list-style: none;
      padding: 0;
    }
    .details li {
      margin: 10px 0;
      padding: 10px;
      background-color: #fff;
      border-radius: 4px;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 0.9em;
      color: #666;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="header">
    <h1>Welcome to Qurieus!</h1>
  </div>
  
  <div class="content">
    <p>Dear {{customerName}},</p>
    
    <p>Thank you for subscribing to our {{plan}} plan. We're excited to have you on board!</p>
    
    <div class="details">
      <h2>Your Subscription Details:</h2>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Plan:</strong> {{plan}}</li>
        <li><strong>Amount:</strong> {{currency}} {{amount}}</li>
        <li><strong>Billing Cycle:</strong> {{billingCycle}}</li>
        <li><strong>Next Billing Date:</strong> {{nextBillingDate}}</li>
      </ul>
    </div>
    
    <p>Please find your invoice attached to this email.</p>
    
    <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to contact our support team.</p>
  </div>
  
  <div class="footer">
    <p>Best regards,<br>The Qurieus Team</p>
  </div>
</body>
</html> 